f 2.4, although it is possible for individual\nsystems to exceed this limit. Our 95% upper limits are at the level expected\nfrom numerical simulations, which likely suggests that the injection of CR at\ncosmological shocks is less efficient than previously assumed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2013 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Sep 2013 06:28:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
