he filament reaches a maximum linear density rate of ~30 Msun\nMyr^-1 pc^-1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2013 20:18:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Mar 2014 23:29:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Jul 2014 23:34:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 11 Jul 2014 20:43:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
