, but they are perhaps less\nimportant than accurately treating non-LTE processes [abridged].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 03:09:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Apr 2014 07:23:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
