in correlated gradients across the sky of the galaxy density and\nthe galaxy photo-z precision. Our correction procedure could also help to\nmitigate some of these systematic effects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Aug 2013 15:52:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2013 14:32:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-06"}
